comments: Ayton (PHX) delivers contact to Gobert (UTA) that causes Gobert to make contact with Mitchell (UTA) during Mitchell's driving shot attempt.
Crowder (PHX) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Bogdanovic (UTA).
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal picking position in O'Neale's (UTA) path.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Johnson (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball at the end of Conley's (UTA) drive.
Paul (PHX) does not deliver any contact to Conley (UTA) as Conley is falling out of bounds to make the pass.
O'Neale (UTA) releases the pass prior to his foot landing out of bounds.
Booker (PHX) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) and Crowder's (PHX) make incidental body contact with one another as they pursue the long rebound.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Conley's (UTA) path.
Conley (UTA) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) legally contests Bogdanovic's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact with the ball then marginal follow-through contact with Johnson's (PHX) wrist/hand during the rebound.
Paul (PHX) briefly grasps Gobert's (UTA) arm during the rebound.
Gobert (UTA) makes slight contact with Booker's (PHX) front after the release of Booker's driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) does not make any contact with Booker (PHX) as he taps the rebound away from Booker.
Crowder (PHX) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) firms up in Mitchell's (UTA) path and does not deliver any contact during the screen.
Mitchell (UTA) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Johnson's (PHX) path and does not deliver any contact.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bookers (PHX) path.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact with Mitchell's (UTA) backside during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) briefly engages then disengages with Ayton (PHX) during the rebound.
On his drive to the basket, Mitchell (UTA) makes foot to foot contact with Gobert (UTA) as they move towards the basket. Any additional contact from Ayton (PHX) is deemed incidental.
Crowder (PHX) makes contact with Conley (UTA) on-ball that impedes Conley's progress.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Johnson (PHX).
In an effort to commit a take foul, Mitchell (UTA) reaches in and makes contact with Booker (PHX) in the backcourt.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Craig (PHX) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA) prior to his upward shooting motion.
Conley (UTA) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
As Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in picking position, he places his arm away from his body and makes marginal contact with Craig (PHX) during the pick.
Crowder (PHX) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
